Class WrapElementImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sam.webelement.WrapElementImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WrapElement, org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext

    EditableWrapElementImpl, LoginImpl, MainImpl, NonEditableWrapElementImpl
    public class WrapElementImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements WrapElement
    Generates a WrapElement object(wrapper for selenium web element) for interactions on test pages.
